        <title>第一巻：東京秋夜雨ーー序</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/jp/p/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%B7%BB%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E7%A7%8B%E5%A4%9C%E9%9B%A8%E3%83%BC%E3%83%BC%E5%BA%8F/</link>
